  ‚à•z - soln‚à• = ‚à•(z - a) + (a - soln)‚à• : by rw sub_add_sub_cancel
        ... ‚â§ max (‚à•z - a‚à•) (‚à•a - soln‚à•) : padic_norm_z.nonarchimedean _ _
