  ‚à•F.derivative.eval soln‚à• = ‚à•(-q) * h‚à• : by rw this
... ‚â§ 1 * ‚à•h‚à• : by rw [padic_norm_z.mul]; exact mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_right (padic_norm_z.le_one _) (norm_nonneg _)
