    ‚à•F.derivative.eval a‚à• = ‚à•q‚à•*‚à•h‚à• : by simp [this]
    ... ‚â§ 1*‚à•h‚à• : mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_right (padic_norm_z.le_one _) (norm_nonneg _)
